msgid "Cooks food and keeps bees happy."
msgstr "Janaria prestatzen du eta erleak zoriontsu mantentzen ditu."

msgid "Campfires have multiple uses, including keeping bees happy, cooking raw meat and fish, and as a trap."
msgstr ""
"Sutegiek erabilera ugari dituzte, besteak beste, erleak zoriontsu "
"mantentzea, haragi gordina eta arraina prestatzea, eta tranpa gisa."

msgid "Campfire"
msgstr "Sua"

msgid "Soul Campfire"
msgstr "Arimen sua"
